import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import statsmodels.api as sm
from pylab import rcParams
rcParams['figure.figsize'] = 15, 7

labels=list(y_train.Label.unique())
plt . figure(figsize=(15,7))

for each_label in labels:
    plt.cla()
    get_one_index=y_train[y_train['Label']==each_label].index[0]
    get_file=X_train.loc[[get_one_index]].values[0][1]
    #print(get_file.values[0][1])
    
    col_sub='EMG1,EMG2,EMG3,EMG4,Airborne,ACC_upper_X,ACC_upper_Y,ACC_upper_Z,Goniometer_X,ACC_lower_X,ACC_lower_Y,ACC_loewr_Z,Goniometer_Y,Gyro_upper_X,Gyro_upper_Y,Gyro_upper_Z,Gyro_lower_X,Gyro_lower_Y,Gyro_lower_Z'
    
    df_explo=pd.read_csv(ruta+'/Subjects/'+get_file,names=col_sub.split(','))
   
    for each_col_signal in col_sub.split(','):
        lowess = sm.nonparametric.lowess
        
        #df_explo[[each_col_signal]]
        anali=np.log(df_explo[[each_col_signal]])
        valores=anali.values
        #print(type(valores.ravel()))
        #print(anali.values.reshape(1,len(anali.values)))
        indice=np.arange(0,len(anali.values),1)
        w = lowess(valores.ravel(), indice, return_sorted=False,is_sorted=True)
        plt.plot(anali.index,w, label=each_col_signal)
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    #plt . xlabel ('Date' , fontdict=font)
    #plt . ylabel ('USD' , fontdict=font)
    plt.title(each_label , fontdict=font)
    plt . legend ( loc='best')
    plt.grid(True) 
    plt.show()
